    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>This collection contains administrative records for the Ridge Road United Church in
        Littleton, Colorado, as well as an extensive collection of scrapbooks documenting the
        history of the church. The administrative records generally contain meeting minutes,
        especially those of the church council. The records also contain some lists of baptisms,
        marriages, and membership. The scrapbooks are extensive and constitute the bulk of the
        collection. They document the history of the church, largely through collected bulletins,
        worship programs, clippings, and photographs. There is also a scrapbook documenting the
        advent of the church Women's Fellowship.</p>
    </scopecontent>
